	<dl>
	<dt>there is too much choice - three party...</dt>
	<dd><p>there is too much choice - three party leaders, each with two faces, is too much to cope with.  I will stay at home and have a nice cup of tea and a biscuit while I fill in my emigration forms.</p>
	<small>
	written 3rd May 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1705">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1705">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

