	<p><em><strong>Nick</strong> replies:</em> Bad news.  If you like a nice cuppa tea, emigration isn't such an attractive option.</p> <p>When you've lived in England, you really don't much fancy what passes for tea elsewhere.  When you've lived in Italy, you don't much fancy what passes for coffee elsewhere.  You might want to lose that caffeine habit!</p>
	<small>
	written 3rd May 2005 <!-- | <a
